FootnoteText: †Data were derived from CDC's School Health Profiles (Profiles). This indicator used one question from the Profiles Principal Questionnaire. Schools where the principal answered, "Yes" to the question, "During this school year, has your school done any of the following: Offered a self-serve salad bar to students?" were classified as having a salad bar.
